_sText:
CREDITS: All to me, CaptrTheBag, and of course Valve!

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
Unzip fy_woodworld.zip
Move the fy_woodworld.bsp file into Steam> SteamApps> Your Acount> counter-strike source> cstrike> maps

DESCRIPTION: This map is basically self explanatory! It is based in a wooden box with some glass to add to the gameplay, but still keeps its deathmatch roots. It is smaller than the average fy map in width and length but it has 3 floors to keep it spread out. Hope you have fun with this map!
